      "content": "but it wasn't just stress. it felt way too specific for that. like, whenever he hit a certain word, the frequency would change, almost like a pitch shift? it was very distinct from my usual anxiety. it felt more like I was picking up on an actual physical property of his voice that was out of sync. does that even make sense from a physics standpoint?",
